script.name: ff_securitycode_ok
script.title: Security code ok
script.description: Check that a valid security code was entered.
script.code:
function ff_securitycode_ok(element\x2C message)
{
\x3C?php
 global $ff_seccode\x3B
 if (!isset($ff_seccode)) { 
 mt_srand((double)microtime()*1000000)\x3B
 $ff_seccode = mt_rand(10000\x2C 99999)\x3B
 JFactory::getSession()-\x3Eset(\x27ff_seccode\x27\x2C $ff_seccode)\x3B
 } // if
 $enc = array()\x3B
 mt_srand((double)microtime()*1000000)\x3B
 for ($i = 0\x3B $i \x3C 256\x3B $i++) $enc[] = mt_rand(0\x2C 255)\x3B
 $seccode = (string)$ff_seccode\x3B
 $hash = \x27\x27\x3B
 $ini = $ff_seccode % 240\x3B
 for ($i = 0\x3B $i \x3C 5\x3B $i++) {
 $d = $ini+intval($seccode{$i})\x3B
 for ($j = 0\x3B $j \x3C 7\x3B $j++) $d = $enc[$d]\x3B
 $hash .= $d\x3B
 $ini = ($ini+$d) % 240\x3B
 } // for
 return
 \x22var enc = \x22.$this-\x3EexpJsValue($enc).\x22\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22var seccode = new String(element.value)\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22if (seccode.length==5) {\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22 var hash = \x27\x27\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22 var ini = parseInt(element.value) % 240\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22 var i\x2C j\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22 for (i = 0\x3B i \x3C 5\x3B i++) {\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22 var d = ini+parseInt(seccode.charAt(i))\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22 for (j = 0\x3B j \x3C 7\x3B j++) d = enc[d]\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22 hash += d\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22 ini = (ini+d) % 240\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22 } // for\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22 if (hash == \x27$hash\x27) return \x27\x27\x3B\x5Cn\x22. 
 \x22} // if\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22if (message==\x27\x27) message = \x5C\x22Security code is missing or wrong.\x5C\x5Cn\x5C\x22\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22ff_validationFocus(element.name)\x3B\x5Cn\x22.
 \x22return message\x3B\x5Cn\x22\x3B
?\x3E
} // ff_securitycode_ok

script.name: ff_validate_date
script.title: Validate Date
script.description:
Validates that the date in a textfield is correctly formatted in the format given as prefix in the error message setup.
Example format definition in the message:

YYYY-MM-DD***-***The actual error message.

The middle part ***-*** indicates the separator being used (dash in this case) and also separates the format from the actual error message.

Can be used with a textfield element and/or the Calendar element.

piece.name: ff_databaseToSelect
piece.title: ff_databaseToSelect
piece.description:
Populates a select field with database stuff. Use like so:

databaseToSelect($select\x2C $table\x2C $label\x2C $value\x2C $sql)\x3B

$label and $value are fields you want to display as label and value in select options. $table
is the name of the table you want to look for. $select is the name of the select input. $sql holds custom SQL query\x2C if supplied. If not\x2C
function will perform a simple \x27SELECT $label\x2C $valueFROM $table\x27\x3B

example\x3B databaseToSelect(\x27mySelect\x27\x2C \x27users\x27\x2C \x27name\x27\x2C \x27ID)\x3B

piece.name: ff_die
piece.title: Terminate form gracefully
piece.description:
Gracefully terminates the form and shows a message plus optionally a 
CONTINUE button for further redirection.

Call:

 ff_die($message=null\x2C $action=\x27stop\x27\x2C $target=\x27\x27\x2C $params=\x27\x27\x2C $label=\x27Continue\x27)\x3B
 return\x3B

 $message = A message to display. If no message is provided\x2C it will
 display:

 Fatal error in $formname\x2C processing stopped.

 $action = \x27stop\x27 : Dont show a CONTINUE button (default)
 \x27self\x27 : Redirect to the same form
 \x27form\x27 : Redirect to another form 
 \x27page\x27 : Redirect to another page of this site
 \x27home\x27 : Redirect to homepage of the site
 \x27url\x27 : Redirect to a url

 $target = Target name/url for \x27form\x27\x2C \x27page\x27 and \x27url\x27

 $params = Additional parameters for \x27self\x27 and \x27form\x27

 $label = Text for the continue button

Examples:

 // Display standard message without continue button
 ff_die()\x3B 

 // Display message without continue button
 ff_die(\x27Sorry\x2C cannot continue for some reason.\x27)\x3B

 // Display standard message and return to same form with a parameter
 ff_die(null\x2C \x27self\x27\x2C \x27\x26ff_param_foo=bar\x27)\x3B

 // Redirect to another form
 ff_die(\x27Guess you are hungry now...\x27\x2C \x27form\x27\x2C \x27SamplePizzaShop\x27\x2C null\x2C \x27Order\x27)\x3B

 // Redirect to another site page
 ff_die(
 \x27Something strange has happened!\x27\x2C 
 \x27page\x27\x2C 
 \x27index.php?option=com_content\x26task=section\x26id=1\x26Itemid=2\x27
 )\x3B
piece.code:
function ff_die($message=\x27\x27\x2C $action=\x27stop\x27\x2C $target=\x27\x27\x2C $params=\x27\x27\x2C $label=\x27Continue\x27)
{
 global $ff_processor\x3B
 if ($ff_processor-\x3Edying) return\x3B

 ob_end_clean()\x3B
 $form =\x26 $ff_processor-\x3Eformrow\x3B
 if (!$message) 
 $message = 
 \x22\x3Cstrong\x3EFatal error in $form-\x3Ename\x2C form processing halted.\x3C/strong\x3E\x22\x3B
 switch ($action) {
 case \x27self\x27: $url = ff_makeSelfUrl($params)\x3B break\x3B
 case \x27form\x27: $url = ff_makeFormUrl($target\x2C $params)\x3B break\x3B
 case \x27page\x27: $url = ff_makePageUrl($target)\x3B break\x3B
 case \x27home\x27: $url = \x22{mossite}\x22\x3B break\x3B
 case \x27url\x27 : $url = $target\x3B break\x3B
 default : $url = \x27\x27\x3B
 } // switch
 
 if ($form-\x3Eclass1 != \x27\x27) echo \x27\x3Cdiv class=\x22\x27.$form-\x3Eclass1.\x27\x22\x3E\x27.nl()\x3B
 echo($message.\x27\x3Cbr/\x3E\x3Cbr/\x3E\x3Cbr/\x3E\x27.nl())\x3B

 if ($url) {
 if (!$ff_processor-\x3Einline) echo \x27\x3Cform action=\x22#redirect\x22\x3E\x27.nl()\x3B
 if ($ff_processor-\x3Einframe) $t = \x27parent\x27\x3B else $t = \x27document\x27\x3B
 echo \x27\x3Cinput type=\x22button\x22 class=\x22button\x22 value=\x22\x27.$label.\x27\x22\x27.
 \x27 onClick=\x22\x27.$t.\x27.location.href=\x5C\x27\x27.htmlentities($url\x2CENT_QUOTES).\x27\x5C\x27\x3B\x22\x27.
 \x27/\x3E\x27.nl()\x3B
 if (!$ff_processor-\x3Einline) echo \x27\x3C/form\x3E\x27.nl()\x3B
 } // if
 if ($form-\x3Eclass1 != \x27\x27) echo \x27\x3C/div\x3E\x27.nl()\x3B
 unset($form)\x3B
 ob_start()\x3B
 $ff_processor-\x3Esuicide()\x3B
} // ff_die

piece.name: ff_getSubmit
piece.title: Get submited data
piece.code:
function ff_getSubmit($name\x2C $default=null)
{
 global $ff_processor\x3B

 switch ((string)$default) {
 case FF_ARRAY: $value = array()\x3B break\x3B
 case FF_LIST : 
 case FF_SLIST:
 case FF_DLIST: $value = \x27\x27\x3B break\x3B
 default : $value = $default\x3B
 } // switch
 foreach ($ff_processor-\x3Esubmitdata as $data)
 if ($data[_FF_DATA_NAME]==$name) {
 $q = \x27\x27\x3B
 switch ((string)$default) {
 case FF_ARRAY:
 $value[] = $data[_FF_DATA_VALUE]\x3B
 break\x3B
 case FF_SLIST:
 $q = \x22\x27\x22\x3B
 case FF_DLIST:
 if ($q==\x27\x27) $q = \x27\x22\x27\x3B
 case FF_LIST:
 if ($q==\x27\x27 \x26\x26 !is_numeric($data[_FF_DATA_VALUE])) $q = \x22\x27\x22\x3B
 if ($value!=\x27\x27) $value.=\x27\x2C\x27\x3B
 $value .= $q.$data[_FF_DATA_VALUE].$q\x3B
 break\x3B
 default:
 return $data[_FF_DATA_VALUE]\x3B
 } // switch
 } // if
 return $value\x3B
} // ff_getSubmit

piece.name: ff_makeFormUrl
piece.title: Make URL to other form
piece.description:
Redirects to another facile form. 

Call: 
 $url = ff_makeFormUrl($name\x2C $params = \x27\x27)\x3B

Example:

 $url = ff_makeFormUrl(
 \x27OtherForm\x27\x2C 
 \x27\x26ff_param_email=\x27.urlencode($email)
 )\x3B
piece.code:
function ff_makeFormUrl($name\x2C $params=\x27\x27)
{
 global $ff_processor\x2C $ff_otherparams\x3B
 $url = \x27\x27\x3B
 switch ($ff_processor-\x3Erunmode) {
 case 2: // preview
 case 1: // backend
 $url .= \x27administrator/index2.php?option=com_breezingforms\x26act=run\x27.
 \x27\x26ff_name=\x27.urlencode($name)\x3B
 if ($ff_processor-\x3Einframe) $url .= \x27\x26ff_frame=1\x27\x3B
 if ($ff_processor-\x3Eborder) $url .= \x27\x26ff_border=1\x27\x3B
 break\x3B
 default: // frontend
 $url .= \x27index.php?ff_name=\x27.urlencode($name)\x3B
 if ($ff_otherparams[\x27option\x27] == \x27com_breezingforms\x27) {
 reset($ff_otherparams)\x3B
 foreach( $ff_otherparams as $prop =\x3E $val)
 $url .= \x27\x26\x27.urlencode($prop).\x27=\x27.urlencode($val)\x3B
 } else
 $url .= \x27\x26option=com_breezingforms\x27\x3B
 if ($ff_processor-\x3Etarget \x3E 1) $url .= \x27\x26ff_target=\x27.$ff_processor-\x3Etarget\x3B
 if ($ff_processor-\x3Einframe) $url .= \x27\x26ff_frame=1\x27\x3B
 if ($ff_processor-\x3Eborder) $url .= \x27\x26ff_border=1\x27\x3B
 if ($ff_processor-\x3Ealign !=1) $url .= \x27\x26ff_align=\x27.$ff_processor-\x3Ealign\x3B
 if ($ff_processor-\x3Etop\x3E0) $url .= \x27\x26ff_top=\x27.$ff_processor-\x3Etop\x3B
 } // switch
 return ff_makePageUrl($url. $params)\x3B
} // ff_makeFormUrl

piece.name: ff_redirect
piece.title: Basic redirection
piece.description:
Basic redirection routine supporting multiple targets and methods.

Call:
 ff_redirect($url [\x2C $target=\x27self\x27 \x2C $method=\x27post\x27])

 $url = The url to redirect to including the parameters appended.

 $target = \x27top\x27\x2C \x27parent\x27\x2C \x27self\x27 or \x27blank\x27

 \x27top\x27 = redirect to the top browser window
 \x27parent\x27 = redirect to the parent frame
 \x27self\x27 = redirect in the same frame (the default)
 \x27blank\x27 = redirect to a new browser window 
 (blank works with post method only)

 $method = \x27post\x27 or \x27get\x27. The default is \x27post\x27.

 Example:

 ff_redirect(
 \x27http://mysite.net/index.php?option=xxx\x26Itemid=33\x27\x2C
 \x27top\x27
 )\x3B
piece.code:
function ff_redirect($url\x2C $target=\x27self\x27\x2C $method=\x27post\x27)
{
 global $ff_processor\x2C $ff_request\x3B
 if ($ff_processor-\x3Edying) return\x3B
 ob_end_clean()\x3B //when debugging change this to ob_end_flush()\x3B
 switch (strtolower($method)) {
 case \x27get\x27: {
 switch (strtolower($target)) {
 case \x27top\x27 :
 case \x27parent\x27: break\x3B
 default : $target = \x27window\x27\x3B //window \x3E document\x2C because cross browser compat\x2C or so I read
 } // switch

piece.name: ff_redirectForm
piece.title: Redirect to other form
piece.description:
Redirects to another facile form. 

Call: 

 ff_redirectForm($name\x2C $params = \x27\x27)\x3B

Example:

 ff_redirectForm(
 $this\x2C 
 \x27SecondForm\x27\x2C 
 \x27\x26ff_param_email=\x27.urlencode($email)
 )\x3B

piece.name: ff_redirectPage
piece.title: Redirect to other page
piece.description:
Redirects to another mambo page. 

Call: 
 ff_redirectPage($params = \x27\x27)\x3B

Example:

 ff_redirectPage(
 \x27index.php?option=com_content\x26task=blogsection\x26id=0\x26Itemid=39\x27
 )\x3B

piece.name: ff_redirectParentX
piece.title: Redirect to parent window
piece.description:
Redirects to the parent window when runing in iframe\x2C otherwise to self. 

ff_redirectParent($url [\x2C $method=\x27post\x27])
 $url = The url to redirect to including the parameters appended.

 $method = \x27post\x27 or \x27url\x27. The default is \x27post\x27.

 Example:

 ff_redirectParent(
 \x27http://mysite.net/index.php?option=xxx\x26Itemid=33\x27\x2C
 \x27url\x27
 )\x3B

piece.name: ff_redirectSelf
piece.title: Redirect to same form
piece.description:
Redirects to the same form. 

Call: 
 ff_redirectSelf($params = \x27\x27)\x3B

Example:
 ff_redirectSelf(\x27\x26ff_param_email=\x27.urlencode($email))\x3B

piece.name: ff_securityImage
piece.title: Security Image
piece.description: Create code to display the security image

piece.name: ff_select
piece.title: Select rows from db
piece.description:
Execute a select query

Include by one of:

 $this-\x3EexecPieceByName(\x27ff_InitUtilities\x27)\x3B
 $this-\x3EexecPieceByName(\x27ff_SubmitUtilities\x27)\x3B
 if (!function_exists(\x27ff_select\x27)) $this-\x3EexecPieceByName(\x27ff_select\x27)\x3B

Call syntax:

 $rows = ff_select($sql)\x3B

 $sql: Sql SELECT-statement to call
 $rows: List of row objects

piece.name: ff_selectValue
piece.title: Select single value from db
piece.description:
Execute query to read a single value

Include by one of:
 $this-\x3EexecPieceByName(\x27ff_InitUtilities\x27)\x3B
 $this-\x3EexecPieceByName(\x27ff_SubmitUtilities\x27)\x3B
 if (!function_exists(\x27ff_selectValue\x27)) $this-\x3EexecPieceByName(\x27ff_selectValue\x27)\x3B

Call syntax:

 $value = ff_selectValue($sql)\x3B

 $sql: Sql SELECT-statement to call
 $value: The value returned by the database

piece.name: ff_setCheckedX
piece.title: Set checkbox/radiobutton checked
piece.description:
Set a radio button or checkbox checked. 

Call: 
 ff_setChecked(\x27name\x27\x2C \x27value\x27)\x3B

piece.name: ff_setSelectedX
piece.title: Set a select list option to *selected*
piece.description:
Sets a select list option to selected. 

Call: 
 ff_setSelected(\x27name\x27\x2C \x27value\x27)\x3B

piece.name: ff_setValueX
piece.title: Set text\x2C textarea\x2C hidden value
piece.description:
Set value of a Static Text\x2C Text\x2C Textarea or Hidden Input. 

Call: 
 ff_setValue(\x27name\x27\x2C \x27value\x27)\x3B
